<p>John and Dave kick off the week with a podcast full of your questions, their answers, combined tips, and valuable stories from the lives of your two favorite geeks! First it&rsquo;s Dave and John answering questions about dealing with multiple iTunes accounts and best practices for prolonging the life of your MacBook or MacBook Pro battery. Then it&rsquo;s follow-ups from previous shows, including PowerLine, application switching, AppleCare and more! Don&rsquo;t miss it &mdash; this episode is free today, so download and enjoy!</p>
